      "description": "Mark a single notification as read.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated tenant session/token (`auth:tenant-api`).\n\n**Path params:**\n- `notification_id`: notification UUID\n\n**Request body:** none\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Sets `read_at` to the current timestamp if not already read.\n- Idempotent \u2014 calling again on an already-read notification is a no-op.\n- Returns 404 if the notification doesn't exist or belongs to another user."
